{"tid":1070880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩迪獲評世界最佳運動員！力壓祖高域+費達拿","createTime":"2019-03-21T03:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T13:20:36.000Z","uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0a62f966e6b1b4d50466141e1c7e20f154d46c","tid":1070880,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"國際體育記者協會（AIPS）進行的投票，皇馬中場摩迪力壓兩大網球名將費達拿和祖高域，當選2018年度世界最佳男運動員。<br />\n<br />\n  該獎項由87個國家的359名體育記者投票選出，摩迪得到了419分，祖高域得到337分，費達拿得到290分。摩迪在2018年拿到了金球獎、世界足球先生、世界盃金球獎、歐洲足協最佳球員等一系列大將，如今他的榮譽室中又多了一個獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n  在最佳女運動員的評選中，美國體操名將拜爾斯得到427分，擊敗了捷克滑雪名將萊德卡和羅馬尼亞網球名將賀拿普當選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba657be176cc8cc5023d161ff0fd5d7cdf3a81c","tid":1070880,"uid":14454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073cea29218c5652eba528e721210fb8aaff8a7f","tid":1070880,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會消費到2020年"},{"pid":"c9c85f42ade6d5f0dfc68592da7624d8b8b6ba0c","tid":1070880,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:47:01.000Z","msg":"sick ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69bdc97ddeb529cee675eff28f0ff240bfcfe61","tid":1070880,"uid":127143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1ba45deae62ae9c94f5966fc1e434cb26f80b8","tid":1070880,"uid":47268,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"摩迪都得咁mola達都得啦"},{"pid":"d3bcc3b2d6f7f16bafc9be6a19dfbf6966a10650","tid":1070880,"uid":107611,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:32